  token 1  → [ 0.19, -0.49,  0.78,  0.05 ]   "hi"      ← similar to "hello"!
  token 2  → [-0.90,  0.34, -0.12,  0.67 ]   "king"
  token 3  → [-0.88,  0.71, -0.09,  0.65 ]   "queen"   ← similar to "king"!
